{"title":"问题-规划 Planning","uid":"fe24996d1d2428bc217d0b396f632e99","slug":"笔记/问题/规划","date":"2024-10-18T10:00:15.000Z","updated":"2025-11-15T17:59:44.826Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/笔记/问题/规划.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/post/笔记/问题/规划/cover.png","content":"<p><a href=\"%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%2F%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%2F%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E5%AF%BC%E8%88%AA\">&lt;返回问题导航</a></p>\n<hr />\n<h1 id=\"一-定义\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#一-定义\"></a> 一. 定义</h1>\n<p>规划是一种推理问题，确定需要执行哪些动作（计划）以使某些条件（目标）为真。</p>\n<p>规划是人工智能的核心：作为通过计算手段研究智能行为的重要领域。</p>\n<p>总体上，规划是一个非常复杂的现实世界问题：解决现实中的规划问题通常充满挑战。</p>\n<h1 id=\"二-例子\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#二-例子\"></a> 二. 例子</h1>\n<h2 id=\"1-经典规划\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#1-经典规划\"></a> 1. 经典规划</h2>\n<p>经典规划(Classical Planning)方法为了简化问题，作出了一些假设：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">假设</th>\n<th>说明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">确定的</td>\n<td>每个动作的结果都是确定的</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">可观察的</td>\n<td>代理能够完全感知环境的状态</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">静态的</td>\n<td>环境只会因代理的动作而改变，不受外部因素的干扰</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"i-规划领域定义语言planning-domain-definition-language\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#i-规划领域定义语言planning-domain-definition-language\"></a> i. 规划领域定义语言（Planning Domain Definition Language）</h3>\n<p>组成成分：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">成分</th>\n<th>说明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">系统状态</td>\n<td>使用流项（fluents）描述，可以是正的或负的谓词</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">目标<br>Goals</td>\n<td>流项的合取</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">动作模式<br>Action schemas</td>\n<td>定义可以改变系统状态的原子操作</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>每个动作模式由以下部分组成：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">成分</th>\n<th>说明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">前置条件<br>Precondition</td>\n<td>动作发生所需满足的条件<br>一个流项的列表</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">效果<br>Effect</td>\n<td>动作对系统状态的改变<br>包括一个删除列表（delete list）和一个添加列表（add list）的流项</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"ii-规划问题planning-problem\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#ii-规划问题planning-problem\"></a> ii. 规划问题（Planning Problem）</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">成分</th>\n<th>说明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">定义</td>\n<td>给定一个规划领域和一个目标</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">目标</td>\n<td>找到一系列动作，将初始状态转换为满足目标的状态</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">解决方法</td>\n<td>可以使用搜索算法来求解</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"2-贝叶斯网络bayesian-networks\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#2-贝叶斯网络bayesian-networks\"></a> 2. 贝叶斯网络（Bayesian Networks）</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>现实生活中的不确定性：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>如果 A 是去年参加了 C++ 模块考试的学生，那么 A 很可能通过了 C++ 考试。</li>\n<li>如果某人 A 发烧且咳嗽，那么 A 很可能患有新冠肺炎。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>概率知识库：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>使用 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">.</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">.</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">.</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mi>N</mi></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P(x_1, x_2, ..., x_N)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.30110799999999993em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">1</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.30110799999999993em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">.</span><span class=\"mord\">.</span><span class=\"mord\">.</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.32833099999999993em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">N</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> 表示关联 N 个事实的概率函数。</li>\n<li>其中 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>x</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x_i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.58056em;vertical-align:-0.15em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.31166399999999994em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">i</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 表示第 i 个事件的概率</li>\n<li>此函数展示了整个系统的联合概率分布。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>挑战：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>当 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>N</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">N</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">N</span></span></span></span> 很大时，此函数会变得非常复杂。</li>\n<li>同时，也不清楚如何构建或具体化该函数。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>网络结构：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>节点(Node)</li>\n<li>概率</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p><a href=\"%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%2F%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%2F%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E5%AF%BC%E8%88%AA\">&lt;返回问题导航</a></p>\n","feature":false,"text":"有关规划问题的定义和例子...","permalink":"/post/笔记/问题/规划","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":998,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"笔记-问题","slug":"笔记-问题","count":3,"path":"api/categories/笔记-问题.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Planning","slug":"Planning","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Planning.json"},{"name":"Bayesian Network","slug":"Bayesian-Network","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Bayesian-Network.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80-%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 一. 定义</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8C-%E4%BE%8B%E5%AD%90\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 二. 例子</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 1. 经典规划</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#i-%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E9%A2%86%E5%9F%9F%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80planning-domain-definition-language\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> i. 规划领域定义语言（Planning Domain Definition Language）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#ii-%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98planning-problem\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> ii. 规划问题（Planning Problem）</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E8%B4%9D%E5%8F%B6%E6%96%AF%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9Cbayesian-networks\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 2. 贝叶斯网络（Bayesian Networks）</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"zExNocs","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/avatar.jpg","link":"/","description":"<p>一个喜欢摸鱼的人。<br>去码头整点薯条。</p>","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"github":{"icon":"/img/svg/github.svg","link":"https://github.com/zExNocs"},"bilibili":{"icon":"/img/svg/bilib